recipe.label: Vegan Avocado Lime Ice Cream Recipe
ingredientLines: 4 cups diced avocado (about 30 ounces from 6 avocadoes)
1 tablespoon grated lime zest from 3 to 4 limes
4 to 6 tablespoons lime juice, to taste, from 3 to 4 limes
